subject: This is Director DAVID ALBERT,
body:

subject: Re: This is Director DAVID ALBERT,
body:
Hello Director David Albert,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I can assure you that I am very much alive and well! It's quite surprising to hear about Mrs. Lucy Doss claiming otherwise. Could you please tell me more about her? How is she related to this matter?

Best wishes,
Norman
